block content

  .hero-sky
    .container
      h1 2017 Fall League Registration
  
  .container.register: .row: .col-md-12

    h3 Summary

    p We'll play games on Saturday mornings at 10am near the beach space by Park & Ocean staring November, 4th and played until December 9th. Our finals would be on December 16th.

    iframe(src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2595.3871114681165!2d-80.10347306511046!3d26.14049539386033!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x6f9406a6e78e90c1!2sPark+%26+Ocean!5e1!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1508698698564" width="100%" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen)

    p Following this league we would transition to a Winter Beach League managed and run by the wonderful Fiasco ladies (more information to follow).

    p games would be 4v4 with either a 3-1 or 2-2 gender ratio. We'll be looking to find a competitive & fun level of play.

    p Registration is open <strong>as of today</strong> and the costs are:

    ul
      li $10 for students
      li $15 for everyone else

    p Registration will close November 1st at midnight.

    hr

    h3 Registration

    .alert.alert-info
      strong Refund Policy: 
      | Should there be an error in your registration (paid for a youth fee when an adult or vice versa), we will provide a refund.  Otherwise we will not be providing refunds.

    p If you see your name on the dropdown as you type your name, please click on it so that we can match your records and get your previous answers to the following questions.

    form#registration(action="register" method="post" autocomplete="off")

      if err
        .alert.alert-danger
          strong Error: 
          span=err

      input#user_id.input-lg.form-control.hidden(type='user_id' autocomplete='false' name='user_id' placeholder='' value=formData.user_id)
      .row
        .col-xs-6
          .form-group
            label(for='firstName') First Name

            input#firstName.input-lg.form-control(type='text' name='name.first' placeholder='' value=formData['name.first'] required)
        .col-xs-6
          .form-group
            label(for='lastName') Last Name
            input#lastName.input-lg.form-control(type='text' name='name.last' placeholder='' value=formData['name.last'] required)

      //- Email
      .form-group
        label(for='email') Email address
        input#email.input-lg.form-control(type='email' name='email' placeholder='' value=formData.email required)

      //- Pairing
      .form-group
        label(for='partner') Partner<br><small>If you would like to pair up with another player for sign-up, write their name here.</small>
        input#partner.input-lg.form-control(type='partner' autocomplete='false' name='partner' placeholder='' value=formData.partner)
        input#partner_id.input-lg.form-control.hidden(type='partner_id' autocomplete='false' name='partner_id' placeholder='' value=formData.partner_id)

      //- Age Group
      #age
        label Are you a:
          .radio
            label
              input(type='radio' name='age' value='Adult')
              |     Adult
          .radio
            label
              input(type='radio' name='age' value='Student')
              |     Student

      //- Participation
      label(for="participation" name="participation") Expected Attendance

      p
        small Knowing how often you plan on being there helps captains pick well-rounded teams

      select#participation.input-lg.form-control(name="participation" value=formData.participation)
        option(value="30") Less than 30%
        option(value="50") Around 50%
        option(value="80" selected="selected") Greater than 80%
      br

      //- Shirt Size
      label(for="shirtSize" name="shirtSize") Shirt Size
      select#shirtSize.input-lg.form-control(name="shirtSize" value=formData.shirtSize)
        option(value="S") S
        option(value="M") M
        option(value="L") L
        option(value="XL") XL
        option(value="XXL") XXL
      br

      //- Skill Level
      label(for="skillLevel" name="skillLevel") Skill Level
      select#skillLevel.input-lg.form-control(name="skillLevel" value=formData.skillLevel)
        option(value='1') 1 - Absolute Beginner
        option(value='2') 2 - Hey wait, what's a flick?
        option(value='3') 3 - Working on throws, basic knowledge of game
        option(value='4') 4 - Pickup player, okay throws
        option(value='5') 5 - Decent backhand & forehand. Little to no club experience
        option(value='6') 6 - Fairly solid backhand & forehand. Some club experience
        option(value='7') 7 - Tourney experience. Several years of club
        option(value='8') 8 - Club level, solid all around, not prone to errors
        option(value='9') 9 - Rock star. spot on throws, awesome D

      br
      h3 Waiver
      .checkbox
        label
          input(type='checkbox', value='' required)
          | I agree to SFLUltimate's <a data-toggle="modal" data-target="#waiver">terms & conditions</a>.

      h3 Payment Information
      #payment-form
      .text-center
        button.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-primary(type='submit') Submit

